Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maison.De.章樫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗称妖馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拥有SS系统的最高级公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实体是 妖怪的返祖一族居住的秘密公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这群千奇百怪的人中 我遇到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的SS 御狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了以前与我通信的是装成蜻蛉的他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 他说了事情原委 并向我道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说 信全都好好地收藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不是他该拥有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想的话 就还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回答说信你好好收着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是写给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了这番话后 他又露出欲哭的表情微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反之塚先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是来帮忙的日子 还是来找爸爸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是顺路经过的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反之塚先生 不要紧吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干这种事 会被人发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 当人面对难以置信的事时大脑会自动补正的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便被手机拍到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只会被当做都市传说 报导在夏天的特别节目上罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.87,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}紧急特报 目击 坐在一反木棉上的少年是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么随便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能在这种地方变回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能因为恶作剧而引来社会慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小孩子骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 看你不太敢见你爸的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进了玄关 就可能撞见在休息厅的爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反之塚先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反之塚先生 和我爸爸一样也是妖怪的返祖一族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的返祖一族 是拥有先祖同样的性质
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连记忆都会继承的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这和重生有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸去世了的话 还会重生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸在来世会和不是妈妈的人结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为不是我爸爸的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为是更单纯的父子吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子想的还真多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候开始这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始的时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说爸爸他们 返祖一族都是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厉害啊 这么远的事情都会担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连晚上吃什么都不考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来埋藏时间胶囊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发言和登场都好冷不丁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么担心的话 给爸爸写信就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么是时间胶囊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是因为看信的人是来世的河住先生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给来世的爸爸写？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 写些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不要和妈妈以外的人结婚”什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“爸爸的孩子只有我一个”什么的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去召集伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事都得大家一起乐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间胶囊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不良少年 谁会陪你玩这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我给渡狸写
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给来世的渡狸写
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 来世的渡狸和来世的我关系不好了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就不会看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 关系当然会好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买写信的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 来世会是怎么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想变成怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想变成中华包子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:05:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆沙 肉馅 比萨 比利时巧克力 奶黄 炖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中华包子里面一直塞满了各种美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子里也想一直塞满这些美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但结果还是被吃掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被吃掉之前 我想一直吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快弄 我都陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这么看我们三个人好像三口之家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样是下垂眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连连 洞挖好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚填好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是马后炮 但在这里挖洞不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是公共土地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是不行的吧 一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说将来这公寓还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.38,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,340)}{\frz345}给未来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 你要不要也参加 凛凛蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 时间胶囊 你是小孩子吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都高中生了还要陪你玩这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想的话就算了 拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 正好桌上摆着信纸信封
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便就参加好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凑巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别误会了 真的是碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好在写附在点心盒上的信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚来的时候说什么别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我想和他人多…接触
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概目前会继续恶言相向 招致你们不快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 反正我很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想后悔也没用了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人问我时间胶囊的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 他说你有空的话也参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 之前的甜瓜最后还是掉地上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也还是个微不足道的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 您这么关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的甜瓜 我也做好防腐珍藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 快吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 您什么时候买的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 午休买的 有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您竟然不顾安危
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 我会永久珍藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去庭院了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去庭院？凛凛蝶小姐也参加这活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又勉强卷进其中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 这次不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我不是这种性格真是抱歉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能否请您先去庭院 稍等我片刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也参加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是多和人接触为好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与人的磨合中才能掌握的技巧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是为了独立才来这里的 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要和别人多接触
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从和这里的人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从和他相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不想再独自逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要活得更像样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想待在御狐神君身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 你写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来世的自己什么的 搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就写了当前的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 搞不懂呢 这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎 你也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你那带缆桩什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有寄托时间胶囊的话吗 真是多愁善感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在给来世的爸爸写信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道该写些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来世的我还是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给这种不知道哪来的大叔写信什么办不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是在相遇中成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的人 事 感情什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能与妈妈和你相遇的我 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太过浪漫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我的爸爸就只有爸爸一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵 可喜可贺 可喜可贺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这满足的笑意是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又知道什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你还蛮善解人意的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始还替你捏把冷汗呢 到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 会不会只是多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主犯是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来玩时间减价
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 时间胶囊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在长期保存的盒子里放进写给未来某人的信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是博学的人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你这人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 挖了也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿要填平哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这样齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 还有御狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶 这封信是不是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是交给御狐神的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说什么附在点心盒上的信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会把时间胶囊的信放在点心盒上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难为情 你写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不想再独自逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要活得更像样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想待在御狐神君身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 突然叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了小凛凛蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少会这么失去理智呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他还没看信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先打个电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出是初学者的速度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你写了什么差不多能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦 你们怎么看都是两情相悦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么沮丧啊 不过哥哥我有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定小双双只是「敬爱」之情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟大了7岁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个男人 怎么看都不像是会重伦理的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yeah 萝莉控 这称号太匹配那臭狐狸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安了安了 别这么沮丧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你再待下去的话 小双双不就来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没做好心理准备 我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:06.83,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}时间回到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是告白了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没有这个打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说告白什么的 最不符合我的性格了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:14.60,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(1580,30,-640,30)}{\move(100,100,200,200,0,3240)}连日常生活都不自觉地恶言相向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你在说什么 少蹬鼻子上脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是和平常的自己完全相反了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是自以为是的想要成为恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感谢他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始想改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他给了我这份勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要变得更像样点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一点点改变 也算报答他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 关机了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要跟他说声我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会妨碍他工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开机就打来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没制定好任何计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:05.88,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}计划1：速攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 别找我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太引人怀疑了 得从根本解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:13.41,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}计划2：总之先说明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信没有深层含义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都没能打通电话的原因是信号不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种解释 怎么看都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:19.52,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}计划3：装作如无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 那封信 没什么特别的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是换个话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先接电话 不然对方会挂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽量自然地辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信没有特别的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想作为工作上的伙伴长期合作什么的有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您现在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青城公园 有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我对你没有什么特别的感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 连我都觉得这借口好假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐您是这么说的 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会这么厚脸皮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有自知之明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从自己的人品 立场 活到现在的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所做的事都不堪入您耳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的自己 能像现在待在您身边就很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:22.91,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}From：白鬼院凛凛蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:22.91,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Sub：WELCOME
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:22.91,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}虽然还有很多不足，但今后请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是别人 而是对「我」写信发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我有多重要 没有比这更幸福的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边说您像圣域般不可侵犯 却又心存妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有祈盼更多的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想想的话是免费的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道了吗 我就是这样的男人 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 御狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌…自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就觉得他哪里很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他总是不经意间自嘲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他露出冰冷的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他看上去很孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我懂 我能懂 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也 讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我开始想改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从发现喜欢上你 就拥有了这份勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你给予我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但以往我为了保护自己 而伤害了很多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稍微能成为你的勇气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就由我来受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你喜欢不上自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱您 我爱您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱您 我爱您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱您...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我说的话能成为你的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这更高兴的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:18:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人在做色色的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人在看...御 御...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闻 对小孩子的情操教育不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐 如同身临梦境般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在听我说的吗 放…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到您信的时候 不能自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么告诫自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话 估计会失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 真的高兴得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去小卖部买冰棍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在吃的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是冰激凌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又回来了 肉便器们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子的话 去海边露营了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放置PLAY S
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你们了 家畜们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为逃得出我的手掌心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜻蛉少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋 跑到这来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要来掺一脚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剖开这个章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛凛蝶 我来帮你涂防晒霜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的伪娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很配你呢 渡狸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 考试怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 姑且说声多亏大家 考得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被没收零食了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您今天想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐 非常适合您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御狐神君 借用下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 您也说喜欢我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没听说你是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想…是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗我也没关系 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这个场合下 随便骗我下也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐 我想要个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要个家 将来有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到了从未见过的遥远的你的过去 想象着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的啊 寂寞得惹人怜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不想敷衍了事 这是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 您这个回答我更高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的日子里 一起慢慢考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间是种重负
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐编织的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御狐神君编织的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来会多次回想起 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.28,0:23:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段漫长的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起编织的漫长岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完
